# CODEOWNERS — Musubi monorepo
#
# GitHub uses this to auto-request reviews when a PR touches a path. At Musubi
# v1 there's one human owner; this file still matters because GitHub enforces
# it as a branch-protection rule once v2 becomes main.
#
# Pattern: <path>  <owner-or-team>  [<owner-or-team> ...]

# Default owner for anything not matched below.
*                                   @ericmey

# Canonical API surface — frozen per version. Extra scrutiny on any change.
/src/musubi/api/                    @ericmey
/openapi.yaml                       @ericmey
/proto/                             @ericmey

# Shared types — only slice-types writes here.
/src/musubi/types/                  @ericmey

# Architecture vault (in-repo). Edits should come with explicit reasoning.
/docs/Musubi/                 @ericmey

# Agent configuration — changes affect every coding agent on the project.
/.claude/                           @ericmey
/AGENTS.md                          @ericmey
/GEMINI.md                          @ericmey
/CLAUDE.md                          @ericmey
/.cursor/                           @ericmey

# CI + branch protection — self-referential.
/.github/                           @ericmey
